high_descs: Turn right and walk out of the room and walk straight and reach the dining table
Take a piece of cloth from the dining table
Rotate 360 degree and walk few steps and turn towards right side and reach the counter top on the right side
Put the cloth on the counter top
Turn towards left and reach the fridge
Open the fridge and take the cloth from it and close the door
Turn towards back and reach the counter top
Put the cloth on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Put the cloth on the counter top

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the dining table.
Pick up cloth from the dining table.
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the counter top.
Place cloth on the counter top.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the fridge.
Pick up cloth from the dining table.
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the counter top.
Place cloth on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Collecting cloth from different places and arranging them on a counter top.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the dining table.
Take the cloth from the dining table.
Turn around and go near the counter top.
Put the cloth on the counter top.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Take another cloth from the fridge.
Turn around and go near the counter top.
Put the cloth on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Collect the cloth and placed it on the counter top.
